pi_vi.py:

This file contains all the code for the gridworld problems using value iteration and policy iteration.

The command:
python pi_vi.py

Simulates all gridworld environments and creates the required policy, outputs and figures for Question 1. Each figure needs to exited before the code continues.

bandits.py:

This file contains all the code for the bandits problems using various exploration algorithms.

The command:
python bandits.py

Simulates all the bandit exploration algorithms and creates the required figures for Question 2. Each figure needs to exited before the code continues.